  "about": "Giselle Gewelle is a Quincy and a member of the Wandenreich's Sternritter with the designation \"Z.\"\n\nGiselle has long, dark-colored hair extending down to the lower back, with two strands sticking up like antennae. His attire is a variation of the Sternritter's typical white uniform, consisting of a trench coat with long sleeves, white shoes, and black leggings.\n\nHis power is called The Zombie. Anyone who has Giselle's blood splattered on them falls under his control, effectively becoming a \"corpse\" and doing whatever Giselle orders them to do. This aspect of the ability does not work on fellow Quincy unless they have already died. Giselle can use his power to heal comrades by using the flesh of the deceased to replace their own.\n\n\n\n\nDespite the feminine look to the character, as well as some of his dialogue, Tite Kubo confirmed that Giselle is a man in his website's Q&amp;A #288.",
  "note": null,
  "source": "anime"
